ZH: 我感到迷茫，好像有一种错觉。
EN: I feel confused, as if there is a kind of illusion.

ZH: 他经历了长时间的疲劳，产生一种错觉。
EN: He experienced a long period of fatigue and developed an illusion.

ZH: 她运动过量后出现了错觉。
EN: She experienced illusions after excessive exercise.

ZH: 在这种沉闷的天气下，我常常有一种错觉，好像时间过得很慢。
EN: In this oppressive weather, I often have an illusion that time passes very slowly.

ZH: 经过长时间的研究，专家们破除了他们最初的错觉。
EN: After extensive research, experts dispelled their initial illusion.

